ionisation lines, predicted by RPC to peak\nwell inside $R_{\\rm BLR}$. The dust inflated disc scenario can also be tested\nbased on the predicted response of $R_{\\rm BLR}$ and the CF to changes in the\nAGN luminosity and accretion rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 18:03:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-20"}
