 basis space modeling through simulation studies,\nand illustrate the method using a biomedical imaging data set in which we\nrelate the distribution of pixel intensities from a tumor image to various\ndemographic, clinical, and genetic characteristics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 18:11:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-02"}
