e too highly ionized. We attribute this to the neglect\nof clumping and/or the distribution of intermediate mass and iron group\nelements. The two sub-$M_{\\rm Ch}$ models, while exploded by different\nmechanisms, can be distinguished in the $J$ and $H$ bands at late times (e.g.,\n$+200$ days).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Oct 2017 20:51:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
