channel\nwidth to the optimal partial array diminishes with increasing blockage, the\noptimal global blockage will also decrease.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Nov 2017 14:33:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 03:46:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 6 Jan 2018 04:13:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-09"}
